<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Zion Sepaihte</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Do hat mel pu di'n ei thuomin,
 Aw, Lal Isu;
 Tui bangin a lien nuoizin gal,
 Gehen zinmang gal mite.

[V2]
 Lal thisan bek puonlap,
 Gal maah zak un;
 Zam puoi tiu Lal sepaihte I hiu,
 Gitloh tuipi kinawk mahleh.

[V3]
 2. Lal sepaih te'n lukhuk khui tiu,
 Gal nuoisieh tieng;
 Vak leh zinmang I kido zing,
 Lal Krista thawkna ziekin ,

[V4]
 3. Nuoi zinmang gal lopi sangin,
 I lopi zawi;
 Thagau gilohaw nuoizin gal ,
 I kap Zion sepaih te'n.

[V5]
 4. Gehen gal hi thisan vanga,
 I zawh tieng leh;
 Ai hitiu zawhna lopi chu ,
 Van Zion khawpi achun.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>150</hymn_number>
</song>